HEADWORD: Ferruminate
<hw>Fer*ru"mi*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>ferruminatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>ferruminare</ets> to cement,
solder, fr. <ets>ferrumen</ets> cement, fr. <ets>ferrum</ets>
iron.]</ety> <def>To solder or unite, as metals.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
